<L>__{interior engineering}
<A>__{as scott, too, hears this, but his reaction is of grim acceptance. not so chief ross; she is horrified.}
<C>__{scott}
<P>__{(with a glance at ross, into intercom)}
<D>__{when, captain?}
<C>__{kirk's intercom voice}
<D>__{on my command.}
<C>__{scott}
<P>__{(somberly, into intercom)}
<D>__{aye, sir.}
<A>__{and scott hits buttons on his console, now moves to step from his station, nearly collides with ross, who clearly is bravely struggling to maintain her poise and dignity:}
<C>__{ross}
<D>__{why has the captain ordered self destruct, sir?}
<C>__{scott}
<P>__{(a beat; gently)}
<D>__{i would say, lass, because he thinks he hopes that when we go up... we'll take v'ger with us.}
